name: Travel Wallet - Gray & White Chevron
description:
This travel wallet has a pocket for your passport, identification card and boarding pass. I used 2 great coordinating fabrics. Perfect for your next international trip, or cruise, when you want everything in one place for ease while traveling.

Don't forget to look at all of the pics, the inside fabric is fun too!!

~Fabric design may vary a bit due to pattern placement

~Stiff interfacing for reinforcement

~Size is 5" x 9" (12.5 x 22.5 cm), when closed

~4th photo shows shots of insides of different wallets, this listing only includes the item in the first 3 photos

~Please notice the cute packaging in the last photo

~I hope you love it!
